<item>
            <title>[OAK-989] Query parser doesn&apos;t decode paths</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OAK-989</link>
                <project id="12313221" key="OAK">Jackrabbit Oak</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The SQL2 parser doesn&apos;t correctly decode the path constraints, which can result in queries with no result.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The fix is to apply a &lt;em&gt;ISO9075#decode&lt;/em&gt; similar to the way Jackrabbit did it.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
