                            <comment id="13756176" author="alex.parvulescu" created="Mon, 2 Sep 2013 17:03:01 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;fixed with rev 1519474.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13756704" author="tmueller" created="Tue, 3 Sep 2013 15:38:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I was trying to write a test case. It works for queries of the form: &lt;tt&gt;/jcr:root/hel_x006c_o/*&lt;/tt&gt;, which is converted to the SQL-2 query&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;select [jcr:path], [jcr:score], * 
from [nt:base] as a 
where ischildnode(a, &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;/hel_x006c_o&apos;&lt;/span&gt;)
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;however it doesn&apos;t work for queries of the form: &lt;tt&gt;//hel_x006c_o&lt;/tt&gt;, which is converted to&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;code panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;codeContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre class=&quot;code-java&quot;&gt;select [jcr:path], [jcr:score], * 
from [nt:base] as a 
where name(a) = &lt;span class=&quot;code-quote&quot;&gt;&apos;hel_x006c_o&apos;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I will try to come up with a solution that covers those cases as well.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="13757534" author="tmueller" created="Wed, 4 Sep 2013 08:00:08 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Revision 1519928: Also use decode for //x and //element(x, *)&lt;br/&gt;
Revision 1519930: Test case&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
